Prometheus Metrics to be given on port 9090 on localhost

CPU Metrics

    node_cpu_seconds_total — Total CPU time broken down by mode (user, system, idle, iowait, etc.)

    node_load1, node_load5, node_load15 — System load averages over 1, 5, and 15 minutes

Memory Metrics

    node_memory_MemTotal_bytes

    node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes

    node_memory_Buffers_bytes

    node_memory_Cached_bytes

    node_memory_SwapTotal_bytes

    node_memory_SwapFree_bytes

Disk Metrics

    node_filesystem_size_bytes — Total disk size

    node_filesystem_avail_bytes — Free space available to non-root

    node_disk_read_bytes_total / node_disk_written_bytes_total — Disk I/O

Network Metrics

    node_network_receive_bytes_total

    node_network_transmit_bytes_total

    node_network_up — Whether the interface is up

System Info

    node_time_seconds — System time

    node_boot_time_seconds — Boot time

    node_uname_info — OS details

    node_exporter_build_info — Node Exporter version info
